								<!-- bodycontent -->
				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">"Epileptic" redirects here. For the graphic novel, see <a href="Epileptic_(graphic_novel)" title="Epileptic (graphic novel)" class="mw-redirect">Epileptic (graphic novel)</a>.</div>
