<li id="cite_note-94"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-94">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Civil Aviation Authority requirements - NPPL <a rel="nofollow" class="external autonumber" href="http://www.caa.co.uk/default.aspx?catid=49&pagetype=90&pageid=12133">[3]</a>, retrieved 06 May 2011</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-Vet10-95"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Vet10_95-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Vet10_95-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation Journal">Thomas, WB (2010 Jan). "Idiopathic epilepsy in dogs and cats". <i>Veterinary Clinics of North America, Small Animal Practice</i> <b>40</b> (1): 161–79. <a href="Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.cvsm.2009.09.004">10.1016/j.cvsm.2009.09.004</a>. <a href="PubMed_Identifier" title="PubMed Identifier" class="mw-redirect">PMID</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19942062">19942062</a>.</span></span></li>
</ol>
