<li>Walker, M. &amp; Shorvon, S. <i>Understanding Epilepsy</i> second edition 2000. Family Doctor Publications. <a href="Special_BookSources/1898205205" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 1-898205-20-5</a>.</li>
